boxLists.title: VSCode
boxLists.content: Visual Studio Code (简称 VS Code / VSC) 是一款免费开源的现代化轻量级代码编辑器，支持几乎所有主流的开发语言的语法高亮、智能代码补全、自定义热键、括号匹配、代码片段、代码对比 Diff、GIT 等特性，支持插件扩展，并针对网页开发和云端应用开发做了优化。软件跨平台支持 Win、Mac 以及 Linux。

boxLists.title: Vue.js Jobs
boxLists.content: VueJobs has been developed by Vue.js and Laravel enthusiasts whose aim is to contribute to the growing community by helping companies find Vue.js talent around the world. When you register with Vue.js jobs, companies will be able to list jobs and developers will have the chance to apply for those jobs.
